#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmin.nanmin of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmin.nanmin:26 of
msgid ""
"**nanmin** -- An tensor with the same shape as `a`, with the specified "
"axis removed.  If `a` is a 0-d tensor, or if axis is None, a tensor "
"scalar is returned.  The same dtype as `a` is returned."
msgstr ""
"**nanmin** -- 一个与 `a` 具有相同形状的张量，但移除了指定轴。如果 `a` 是 "
"0 维张量，或者 axis 为 None，则返回张量标量。返回与 `a` 相同的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmin.nanmin of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmin.nanmin:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`nanmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmin.nanmin:34 of
msgid "The maximum value of an array along a given axis, ignoring any NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的数组最大值，忽略任何 NaN。"

