msgid ":py:obj:`amin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmin.nanmin:37 of
msgid "The minimum value of an array along a given axis, propagating any NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的数组最小值，传播任何 NaN。"

