msgid ":py:obj:`fmin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmin.nanmin:40 of
msgid "Element-wise minimum of two arrays, ignoring any NaNs."
msgstr "两个数组的逐元素最小值，忽略任何 NaN。"

